title: Make Yourself at Home at Kenwood Gables Apartments
posting_body: ['Welcome home!', 'Schedule a Tour!', 'Book an appointment online at 2tour.site/OHN/NJRB', 'Kenwood Gables is in the Kenwood/Lowry Hill neighborhood.', 'Enjoy underground parking, a car wash station, fitness center, smoke-free and controlled entry property.', 'Many of our apartment homes offer large walk-in closets, panoramic views, stainless steel appliances, in-unit laundry, and open floor plans -with plenty of space for your home office and fiber-optic internet service is available!', 'Visit today and see why you will love to call Kenwood Gables home!', 'Home Amenities', 'Fiber-optic internet service available', 'Wall air conditioning', 'Washer and dryer - in select homes', 'Balcony or patio options', 'Window coverings', 'Additional storage', 'Smoke free', 'Appliances in kitchen', 'Walk-in closet', 'Community Amenities', 'Pet friendly - some restrictions apply', 'Elevator access', 'Trash chutes', 'Fitness center', 'Party room', 'Business center', 'Off street parking', 'Organized community activities', '24 hour emergency maintenance', 'Car wash station', 'Kenwood Gables Apartments Information', 'Address:', '700 Douglas Ave, Minneapolis MN, 55403', 'Phone:', 'show contact info', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'Details/?pid=14', 'Deposit:', '(Note: Deposit is the same as 1 months rent)', 'Application Fee:', '$45', 'Pet Fee:', '$100 - 200 (Note: varies with pet type)', 'Pet Deposit:', '$200', 'Office Hours', 'Monday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Tuesday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Wednesday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Thursday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Friday:', '9:00AM - 5:00PM', 'Saturday:', '10:00AM - 3:00PM', 'Sunday:', '12:00PM - 3:00PM']
